Dave Willis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dave_Willis 0 Dave Willis (born May 1, 1970) is an American voice actor, writer, producer and musician. He is best known as the co-creator of the Adult Swim animated series Aqua Teen Hunger Force and Squidbillies, the former of which he also voices the characters of Meatwad and Carl Brutananadilewski. He is also known for voicing Barry Dylan in the FXX series Archer and Leto Otel in Ballmastrz: 9009. Dave_Willis ( born May_1_,_1970 ) is an_American_voice_actor , writer_,_producer_and_musician .
